query:
SELECT 
  q.id as questionnaire_id,
  q.title,
  COUNT(qq.id) as question_count
FROM questionnaires q
LEFT JOIN questions qq ON qq.questionnaireId = q.id
WHERE q.id = (
  SELECT tq.questionnaireId 
  FROM partnerQuestionnaires pq
  LEFT JOIN touchpointQuestionnaires tq ON pq.touchpointQuestionnaireId = tq.id
  WHERE pq.accessCode = 'DDSETM9RNAHB'
  LIMIT 1
)
GROUP BY q.id, q.title
